                                                                                                      PROTECTION STRATEGY
                                                                                                      Designing for Cyber Resiliency and Survivability.
                                                                                                      ADVERSARY EFFECTS
                                                                                                      See [SP 800-160-2]: [Redirect (Deter); Preclude (Preempt); Impede (Contain, Degrade, Delay,
